        },
        "subject": "LU-11170 tests: stop running sanity 415 for ZFS",
        "message": "LU-11170 tests: stop running sanity 415 for ZFS\n\nWith ZFS 0.8.1, sanity test 415 is failing an excessive\nnumber of times; over 30% of the time.  We need to stop\nrunning sanity test 415 for ZFS, put it on the ALWAYS_EXCEPT\nlist, until we understand how to fix this issue.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial fstype=ldiskfs testlist=sanity\nTest-Parameters: fstype=zfs testlist=sanity\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <jnunez@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I735872e3d58e29f0e15ad8435856d9ef0fa2d893\n"
      },
